direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **/export-rubric**

  - No arguments
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Processing ---

resolve: |md
  **Resolve Plugin Root**

  - Locate SKILL.md path
  - Navigate two levels up
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

export: |md
  **Run export_rubric.py**

  - Extract rubric from
    agent_prompt.md
  - Write artifacts/rfe-rubric.md
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Output ---

confirm: |md
  **Confirm Output**

  - Verify file written
  - Print file path
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Flow ---

entry -> resolve
resolve -> export: "plugin root path"
export -> confirm: "artifacts/rfe-rubric.md"
